```bash
--dependencies '["redis"]' \
--setup-code 'await redis.connect("redis://localhost:6379")'
```

### External APIs
```bash
--dependencies '["external-api"]' \
--setup-code 'apiClient = new ApiClient("https://api.example.com")'
```

